{"tid":1942508,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【小豬比好可愛】陳展鵬為女慶祝1歲生日 因疫情唔大搞派對","createTime":"2020-03-25T06:08:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T06:08:29.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"884dafa34d852cccf5d14b4d90ec39759d38c675","tid":1942508,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T06:08:29.000Z","msg":"陳展鵬與單文柔去年誕下囡囡陳諾瑤（小豬比），兩夫婦昨日為她慶祝1歲生日，派對以彩色獨角獸公仔為主題，佈置擺了不少彩色波波，作為壽星女的小豬比換了兩條裙仔，戴上粉紅花花頭箍扮靚，兩公婆就分別在社交平台分享。<br />\n<br />\n單文柔分別出了兩個帖文，分別是她抱住小豬比合照及小豬比坐在BB椅的單人相，她表示沒有為女兒大搞生日派對，更代小豬比寫生日願望是希望疫症快點過，而她留言：「時間過得很快，眨下眼已經一年，你出世感覺好似上個月的事，這一年你給我很大轉變，你的笑容，給我勇氣，給我正能量，Love u so much !!! 今年簡簡單單就好，明年再和你搞生日party。」而陳展鵬就擺了一條抱實小豬比的短片，而小豬比更鬼馬地伸脷仔甜笑，他留言：「爸爸應承你喺我有生之年，都會令你開心快樂，小豬比1歲生日快樂。」<br />\n<br />\n此外，兩公婆的藝人朋友如陳山聰、楊秀惠、陳敏之、張繼聰等人都有留言祝福Happy Birthday，而陳展鵬代囡囡回覆：「Quinta，也祝各位哥哥姐姐，百毒不侵，身體健康。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200325/large/1585104819_c14e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200325%2Flarge%2F1585104819_c14e.jpg&h=0a2438ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200325/large/1585104819_bf87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200325%2Flarge%2F1585104819_bf87.jpg&h=61557de4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200325/FO7IZDMKT6NQGHOTTXLXA35QO4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200325%2FFO7IZDMKT6NQGHOTTXLXA35QO4%2F&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2Byn6xOsK%2BJamotDVaNSe1I1zI%3D&h=c5fc17d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200325%2FFO7IZDMKT6NQGHOTTXLXA35QO4%2F&h=d94c7ecf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200325/FO7IZDMKT6NQGHOTTXLXA35QO4/</a><br 